data.description: Price improvement just in time for Christmas! Original owners and first time on the market, located in a quiet cul de sac in a sought after neighborhood. Put an exclamation mark on 2023 with this absolutely stunning home that has it all! RV parking, inground pool, outdoor kitchen, man cave/she shed, hot tub, covered back patio, all situated on .32 of an acre. As you walk inside you're greeted by a spacious living room with fireplace that passes through to the dining room. There is a half bath downstairs and indoor laundry with additional storage. Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom with tons of natural light, a walk in closet, dual vanity's and coffered ceiling. Two nice sized guest bedrooms and a show stopping enormous great room that could be used as a 4th bedroom if desired. This amazing property must be seen to be truly appreciated! Schedule your tour today!
